  GET  /api/v1/pa/:id
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Performance:</b>
  • Page load: <2s (P95)
  • API latency: <500ms
  • Lighthouse: 95+
end note

note right of MobileAPI
  <b>MOBILE API</b>
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  • FastAPI 0.104
  • Python 3.11
  • Pydantic validation
  • JWT authentication
  • 3-8 replicas
  • 25% of traffic
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
