  • Push notifications
  • Offline mode
  • Image compression
  • Biometric auth
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Performance:</b>
  • Latency: <100ms
  • Throughput: 5K req/s
end note

note right of ProviderPortal
  <b>PROVIDER PORTAL</b>
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  • Angular 16
  • NestJS 10.2
  • PrimeNG 16
  • NgRx state mgmt
  • 3-10 replicas
  • 10% of traffic
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Features:</b>
  • Bulk PA submission
  • CSV upload (1K PAs)
  • Analytics dashboard
  • EHR integration
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Performance:</b>
  • Bulk: 50 PAs/sec
  • Dashboard: <3s load
end note

note left of EDIGateway
  <b>EDI GATEWAY</b>
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  • Go 1.21
  • X12 HIPAA 5010
  • HL7 FHIR R4
  • AS2/SFTP/HTTPS
  • 2-5 replicas
  • 3% of traffic
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Transactions:</b>
  • X12 278 (PA Request)
  • X12 997 (ACK)
  • X12 837 (Claims)
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Performance:</b>
  • 2K tx/hour
  • <500ms latency
  • <0.1% error rate
end note

note left of FaxOCR
  <b>FAX OCR SERVICE</b>
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  • Python 3.11
  • Azure Form Recognizer
  • OpenCV 4.8
  • Twilio Fax
