  1. Receive fax (TIFF)
  2. Pre-process image
  3. Azure OCR
  4. Extract fields
  5. Validate data
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  <b>Accuracy:</b>
  • Printed: 98.5%
  • Handwritten: 92%
  • Time: 15-30s/page
end note

note left of VoiceIVR
  <b>VOICE IVR SERVICE</b>
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
