'===================================================================
' LEGEND
'===================================================================
legend bottom right
  <b>═══════════════════════════════════════════════════</b>
  <b>PRESENTATION LAYER - CHANNEL SERVICES</b>
  <b>═══════════════════════════════════════════════════</b>
  
  |= Service |= Technology |= Port |= Traffic % |
  | Web Portal | React 18 + Next.js 14 | 3000 | 60% |
  | Mobile API | FastAPI (Python) | 8001 | 25% |
  | Provider Portal | Angular 16 + NestJS | 3001 | 10% |
  | EDI Gateway | Go 1.21 + X12 | 8002 | 3% |
  | Fax OCR | Python + Azure OCR | 8003 | 1.5% |
  | Voice IVR | Node.js + Azure Speech | 8004 | 0.5% |
  
  <b>Traffic Distribution:</b>
  • Total: 50,000 PA requests/day
  • Peak: 2,500 requests/hour
  • Channels: Web (30K), Mobile (12.5K), Provider (5K), EDI (1.5K), Fax (750), IVR (250)
  
  <b>Deployment:</b>
  • Platform: Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)
