  <b>Performance SLAs:</b>
  • Uptime: 99.95%
  • Web latency: <2s page load (P95)
  • API latency: <500ms (P95)
  • OCR accuracy: 98.5% (printed), 92% (handwritten)
  • STT accuracy: 94%
  
  <b>Security:</b>
  • TLS 1.3 (in transit)
  • AES-256 (at rest)
  • OAuth 2.0 + JWT
  • HIPAA compliant
  
  <b>Connection Types:</b>
  • <color:blue>━━━</color> Main workflow path (thick blue)
  • - - - Secondary connections (dashed gray)
  • <color:green>- - -</color> External integrations (dashed green)
  
  <size:9><i>Last Updated: June 2026 | Version: 1.0</i></size>
endlegend

@enduml
